name: Red Pilled
description: A rendition on my favorites scene in one of my favorite Films. "This is your last chance. After this there is no turning back. You take the blue pill, the story ends; you wake up in your bed and believe whatever you want to believe. You take the red pill, you stay in Wonderland and I show you how deep the rabbit hole goes." "Remember, all I’m offering is the truth, nothing more."
